root.logger=${ZOO_LOG4J_PROP}\" \\\n      -cp $CLASSPATH $JVMFLAGS \\\n-     org.apache.zookeeper.server.PurgeTxnLog $dataDir\n+     org.apache.zookeeper.server.PurgeTxnLog $ZOODATADIR $*\n+else\n+java \"-Dzookeeper.log.dir=${ZOO_LOG_DIR}\" \"-Dzookeeper.root.logger=${ZOO_LOG4J_PROP}\" \\\n+     -cp $CLASSPATH $JVMFLAGS \\\n+     org.apache.zookeeper.server.PurgeTxnLog $ZOODATALOGDIR $ZOODATADIR $*\n+fi\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=fern","name":"fern","key":"fern","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Fernando Padilla","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2009-07-17T19:07:07.668+0000","updated":"2009-07-17T19:07:07.668+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12430805/comment/12732718","id":"12732718","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=mahadev","name":"mahadev","key":"mahadev","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Mahadev konar","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"fernando,\n can you please upload the patch in a file... \n\njust go to zookeeper-3.2.0/ directory and do an svn diff > patchfile.txt.\n\nThen upload the file via attach file link on the left hand side of this page.\n\nThis way you will have to click on a button agreeing to donate your code to apache. This way we do not have any legal issues